FYI in bootstrap 3 we got four major breakpoints as below:

**lg:** Large devices Desktops (≥1200px)

**md:** Medium devices Desktops (≥992px)

**sm:** Small devices Tablets (≥768px)

**xs:** Extra small devices Phones (&lt;768px)

